33:14.159 --> 33:15.240
She was never enrolled.

33:16.203 --> 33:18.160
There's something that I considered
showing the police,

33:18.246 --> 33:19.737
but they never came by to ask.

33:20.248 --> 33:23.286
I don't even know if it's important,
but for some reason I kept it.

33:33.220 --> 33:34.756
That's Jennifer with Marcy.

34:01.623 --> 34:02.454
Stop.

34:04.376 --> 34:05.366
Back it up.

34:07.712 --> 34:08.748
There. Stop.

34:11.382 --> 34:14.717
<i>Okay, Marcy Williams,
Mercedes four-door, right?</i>

34:14.803 --> 34:15.668
Yeah, that's right.

34:17.054 --> 34:18.045
Okay.

34:18.556 --> 34:21.174
Here we go, got it!

34:22.101 --> 34:23.092
Not on file.

34:23.603 --> 34:26.094
That's a red flag.
Usually means government issue.

34:26.648 --> 34:27.684
What agency?

34:27.774 --> 34:29.106
<i>Your guess is as good as mine.</i>

34:30.068 --> 34:31.058
Anything else?

34:31.152 --> 34:34.896
<i>There are 14 licenses issued
under the name "Marcy Williams."</i>

34:34.989 --> 34:37.107
<i>Forty-two under "Marshell Williams."</i>

34:37.199 --> 34:38.940
<i>If you give me an age, I can crosscheck.</i>

34:39.911 --> 34:41.527
Tell you what, I'll let you know.

34:42.330 --> 34:43.320
Hey, G.

34:43.998 --> 34:45.114
<i>Yeah?</i>

34:45.208 --> 34:46.197
I'm glad you're out.

34:46.918 --> 34:47.998
Yeah, me too.

36:01.951 --> 36:02.941
Hello, Marcy.

36:03.286 --> 36:04.868
Actually, it's Rebecca.

36:05.622 --> 36:07.204
- Gallagher.
- I know.

36:07.957 --> 36:09.539
