of Jennifer Pierce shut down.

36:20.387 --> 36:21.844
I know you were sleeping with Jennifer.

36:21.930 --> 36:24.343
I bet there was no love lost there
when she was murdered.

36:26.059 --> 36:27.095
Anything else?

36:28.395 --> 36:29.806
I liked you better as a blonde.

36:30.897 --> 36:31.887
Give it time.

36:33.066 --> 36:34.056
I don't think so.

36:34.484 --> 36:36.271
Why are you tracking Bill Pierce?

36:36.361 --> 36:37.522
That's my business.

36:39.322 --> 36:40.529
This is who I work for.

36:41.825 --> 36:43.032
That should scare you.

36:43.993 --> 36:45.529
It scares the hell out of me.

36:45.620 --> 36:46.952
What's it got to do with Pierce?

36:47.330 --> 36:49.413
