- He's got a young mistress.

37:11.938 --> 37:13.895
He buys her gifts, expensive jewelry,

37:13.982 --> 37:16.645
got a nice place down on the waterfront
with her shacked up.

37:17.152 --> 37:19.439
Be nice to know where he's getting
all that money from.

37:20.280 --> 37:23.864
You sticking your nose into this
is only going to make things worse.

37:24.242 --> 37:26.780
Well, it couldn't get much worse
for Jennifer Pierce, could it?

37:27.620 --> 37:29.202
By the way, you sleeping with her,

37:29.289 --> 37:32.202
was that for God and country and all that
or was that for real?

37:42.927 --> 37:43.917
Eddie!

37:44.304 --> 37:46.546
You want it done right
or you want it done?

37:46.639 --> 37:48.346
And put that cigarette out.

37:49.684 --> 37:50.765
On second thought...

37:54.189 --> 37:55.305
give it here.

37:58.401 --> 37:59.391
What do we got?

38:02.030 --> 38:03.066
Professional.

38:06.409 --> 38:08.492
- Only one?
- That I could find.

38:08.953 --> 38:10.660
You piss somebody off again?

38:11.706 --> 38:13.072
It's a problem of mine.

38:38.650 --> 38:40.186
Put your dick-hands where I can see 'em.

38:41.152 --> 38:41.983
Problem, officer?

38:42.070 --> 38:44.904
- License and registration.
- Okay if I reach into my jacket?

38:44.989 --> 38:47.072
Shut the fuck up and get out the car!

38:54.207 --> 38:55.243
Come on. Let's go.

38:56.084 --> 38:59.373
You know, you two dick twins
are the second team to stop me like this.

38:59.462 --> 39:00.293
"Dick twins?"

39:00.380 --> 39:01.712
Is that what you said, "Dick twins?"

39:01.798 --> 39:04.131
Do you fuckin' think
I look like this fuckin' Uncle Tom?

39:04.217 --> 39:07.130
You think I look like this trailer trash,
inbred motherfucker?

39:07.554 --> 39:08.670
I didn't say that.

39:09.055 --> 39:10.762
You going to jail, scumbag.

39:10.849 --> 39:13.216
- I've been to jail I, didn't like it.
- You like your teeth?

39:13.309 --> 39:14.971
'Cause you're about to lose
a couple molars.

39:15.061 --> 39:16.472
Just tell me what I did wrong.

39:16.563 --> 39:18.725
Well, for starters,
driving with a broken taillight.

39:23.152 --> 39:24.859
