39:47.719 --> 39:48.550
You see that?

39:49.429 --> 39:51.671
That's a dashcam
uploading everything we say and do

39:51.764 --> 39:53.551
directly to my attorney's server.

39:54.350 --> 39:56.137
That's right, you dumb motherfuckers,

39:56.853 --> 39:58.094
I own you.

39:58.521 --> 39:59.978
So this is what's gonna happen.

40:00.064 --> 40:01.896
You're gonna go back to the precinct,

40:01.983 --> 40:05.397
and you're gonna tell
your fuckhead buddies to back off.

40:07.405 --> 40:08.816
You owe me for a taillight.

40:42.941 --> 40:43.931
Back off!

41:35.535 --> 41:36.525
All right.

41:36.619 --> 41:37.860
We're just about done here.

41:38.246 --> 41:39.407
Anything else you could think of?

41:39.497 --> 41:40.613
Like what?

41:40.707 --> 41:42.790
Like maybe why someone
would wanna kill you.

41:43.459 --> 41:45.325
Aside from half the cops in this city?

41:45.795 --> 41:46.785
Aside from them.

41:46.879 --> 41:48.586
'Cause any of them
woulda done a better job

41:48.673 --> 41:49.914
than what happened here tonight.

41:50.550 --> 41:51.882
Nobody I can think of.

41:53.428 --> 41:54.509
All right. Thanks, doc.

41:55.096 --> 41:58.055
Keep in mind what I got from you
is only one side of the story.

41:58.641 --> 42:00.177
The true side, Frank.

42:01.728 --> 42:04.220
The side that used to count
for something in this city.

42:04.480 --> 42:06.472
After we get the ballistics in on the gun

42:06.566 --> 42:09.024
and find out something
about this guy you say ran off,

42:09.110 --> 42:10.351
we gonna be talkin' again.

42:10.987 --> 42:12.819
Hey, Frank, you get a hit on that gun,

42:13.156 --> 42:14.897
