42:17.285 --> 42:18.617
What are you, a cop or something?

42:19.078 --> 42:20.410
Let me tell you something, tough guy.

42:20.496 --> 42:23.489
If I find even a smidge of something
I can arrest you for,

42:23.583 --> 42:24.414
I will bury you.

42:24.500 --> 42:26.787
I will fuckin' bury you
and enjoy doing it.

42:27.211 --> 42:29.203
You think I say that
'cause you a bent cop?

42:29.547 --> 42:32.506
