a good cop?

42:33.718 --> 42:34.925
Thought crossed my mind.

42:35.470 --> 42:36.301
You'd be wrong.

42:37.096 --> 42:38.712
I'll say that 'cause you a scumbag.

42:39.640 --> 42:41.051
Ask me why you a scumbag.

42:41.601 --> 42:42.842
Why am I a scumbag?

42:43.269 --> 42:47.013
Because I've been on the job
18 years, nine months, and 22 days,

42:47.565 --> 42:49.022
