43:11.047 --> 43:12.037
Have a nice evening.

43:12.590 --> 43:13.546
Hey, Frank!

43:14.092 --> 43:15.628
You got a card?

43:16.511 --> 43:17.877
Just in case I have any questions

43:17.970 --> 43:19.962
or in the unlikely event
that you're not as lousy

43:20.056 --> 43:21.592
at your job as I think you are?

43:24.811 --> 43:25.767
All out.

43:45.873 --> 43:46.704
<i>Hello?</i>

43:47.208 --> 43:49.575
You put a tracking device
underneath my car.

43:50.002 --> 43:52.790
<i>And you took it out, which means
I'm gonna have to put it back.</i>

43:53.339 --> 43:54.830
Someone just tried to kill me.

43:56.175 --> 43:57.632
<i>I don't know anything about that.</i>

43:58.136 --> 44:00.344
I'm sure you don't,
but if it happens again,

44:00.429 --> 44:02.136
I'll be sending your little package
to the media

44:02.223 --> 44:04.715
with everything I know
about the Jennifer Pierce case.

44:04.809 --> 44:06.095
<i>And who the fuck gonna tr...</i>

44:19.866 --> 44:21.402
Who's on the phone?

44:25.246 --> 44:27.784
Who is this, and why you callin'
in the middle of the night?

44:27.874 --> 44:28.705
<i>Jimmy?</i>

44:29.750 --> 44:30.991
Who is it, Jimmy?

44:31.919 --> 44:33.160
Yeah, hold on a second.

44:34.672 --> 44:35.583
Jimmy, who is it?

44:35.882 --> 44:37.418
It's okay. I got this. Go to bed.

44:41.888 --> 44:44.096
Hey, you better be callin' me
'cause you hit the lotto,

44:44.182 --> 44:45.263
because anything else

44:46.392 --> 44:47.599
