44:48.394 --> 44:49.384
I need a favor.

44:50.188 --> 44:51.019
What's up?

44:51.439 --> 44:53.726
<i>I may have a lead on what happened
that night with Driscoll.</i>

44:55.109 --> 44:56.145
<i>I need files, though.</i>

44:56.402 --> 45:00.237
<i>Unsolved homicide, three years ago,
woman named Jennifer Pierce.</i>

45:01.574 --> 45:02.735
I'll see what I can do.

45:05.161 --> 45:07.403
Meet me at the Anaconda,
1:00, you're buying.

45:09.498 --> 45:10.363
Shame on you, Jimmy.

45:15.046 --> 45:17.254
What am I supposed to do?
Turn my back on him?

45:17.882 --> 45:18.713
Yes.

45:19.342 --> 45:21.129
That's exactly what you're supposed to do.

45:26.140 --> 45:27.551
Just walk away from it.

45:30.144 --> 45:30.975
Please.

45:33.105 --> 45:33.936
Jimmy.

45:38.110 --> 45:39.476
- What about us?
- What ab...

45:39.570 --> 45:41.482
What about all the conversations?

45:47.286 --> 45:48.117
Please.

45:49.956 --> 45:51.037
I'm all he's got.

46:06.138 --> 46:07.754
This place is all fished out.

46:08.516 --> 46:10.382
So I know I haven't lost my touch.

46:16.899 --> 46:18.435
What you wanted on the car bombing.

46:20.569 --> 46:22.686
It's an ongoing investigation so...

46:23.864 --> 46:26.777
The material's highly sensitive,
which means don't ask any questions,

46:26.867 --> 46:29.109
which also means
get the fuck out of my face.

46:29.996 --> 46:32.033
The materials on the forensics that was,

46:32.123 --> 46:33.364
that was more difficult.

46:33.457 --> 46:35.540
Luckily, I had a buddy in forensics.

46:35.626 --> 46:37.492
Somebody shut down access.

46:37.586 --> 46:39.748
- Any idea who?
- Yeah, somebody high up.

46:42.717 --> 46:43.753
What's it all about?

46:46.262 --> 46:48.970
Charlie was working something
on a guy named Pierce.

46:49.056 --> 46:51.048
Husband of the woman who got blown up.

46:51.434 --> 46:53.266
I think that's why Driscoll killed him.

46:53.352 --> 46:54.684
Charlie found out what they were into.

46:56.605 --> 46:58.221
Whatever you're chasing is a dead end.

47:02.361 --> 47:03.897
You have any idea what kind of money

47:03.988 --> 47:06.196
Charlie was into the Shylocks
in this town for?

47:07.283 --> 47:08.569
Forty-two five.

47:09.452 --> 47:11.910
Forty-two five
to three different Shys in this town,

47:11.996 --> 47:13.737
