that gets you bent.

47:15.750 --> 47:16.706
April sixth.

47:16.792 --> 47:18.203
- Still on?
- Still on.

47:18.711 --> 47:20.919
You go after Driscoll,
I can't help you, Danny.

47:21.005 --> 47:21.995
You understand that?

47:22.798 --> 47:23.914
I don't want your help.

47:25.176 --> 47:28.260
I don't give a fuck if you want it or not,
I still can't do it.

47:28.346 --> 47:31.259
But I can go back to my original advice,
which is go find Kate,

47:31.974 --> 47:33.715
go to Paraguay

47:33.809 --> 47:36.472
or some godforsaken country
nobody can pronounce,

47:37.521 --> 47:38.762
and make a life for yourself.

47:42.526 --> 47:43.812
<i>Phyllis, it's Gallagher.</i>

47:44.904 --> 47:45.985
Yes?

47:46.072 --> 47:47.859
I need to get a court transcript quickly.

47:48.407 --> 47:49.989
- We know anybody?
<i>- We do.</i>

47:50.076 --> 47:51.157
<i>Whose transcript?</i>

47:51.660 --> 47:52.650
Mine.

48:18.938 --> 48:19.849
Casey.

48:22.691 --> 48:23.681
Just checking in.

48:24.151 --> 48:25.232
Wondering how it's goin'.

48:26.195 --> 48:27.356
How'd you know where I live?

48:27.863 --> 48:28.728
Alexis.

48:29.198 --> 48:31.315
She mentioned it
when I dropped her off at the airport.

48:32.118 --> 48:33.154
She went home, you know?

48:33.744 --> 48:34.655
Yeah.

48:36.288 --> 48:37.278
So?

48:37.623 --> 48:38.955
Well, Pierce doesn't work
for the Treasury.

48:39.041 --> 48:41.533
I don't know what the hell he does,
but he ain't no accountant.

48:41.752 --> 48:42.833
I don't understand.

48:44.171 --> 48:46.128
- Where's your sister's car?
- What?

48:47.091 --> 48:48.377
The bomb blew up Pierce's car.

48:48.467 --> 48:50.174
Why wasn't your sister driving her own?

48:50.261 --> 48:51.422
