48:51.762 --> 48:54.220
- You know where it is now?
- No. I don't know.

48:54.306 --> 48:55.592
Do you have any idea

48:55.683 --> 48:58.596
why Pierce goes to a church
all the way over in Seidel?

49:00.020 --> 49:02.012
Bill Pierce?
He never went to church in his life.

49:03.149 --> 49:04.310
He's an atheist.

49:05.901 --> 49:07.733
<i>Pray my brothers and sisters,</i>

49:07.820 --> 49:10.904
<i>that our sacrifice
may be acceptable to God,</i>

49:11.490 --> 49:12.651
the Almighty Father.

49:13.242 --> 49:15.450
May the Lord accept
this sacrifice at your hands,

49:15.536 --> 49:18.370
for the praise and glory of his name,

49:18.956 --> 49:20.322
for our good,

49:20.416 --> 49:22.829
and for the good of all his church.

49:23.294 --> 49:24.626
Amen.

49:39.935 --> 49:40.925
Hey, buddy!

49:41.020 --> 49:41.851
You got a minute?

49:41.937 --> 49:42.927
I'm busy at the moment.

49:44.565 --> 49:45.851
Great mass.

49:46.400 --> 49:47.311
I remember you.

49:48.027 --> 49:49.734
I remember everyone
who gives a nice donation.

49:50.279 --> 49:51.190
Gotta tell ya, buddy,

49:51.280 --> 49:54.444
I really enjoyed listening to that priest
who was here the other day.

49:54.533 --> 49:55.694
He was amazing!

49:56.160 --> 49:57.367
Father Bailey's the best.

49:57.745 --> 49:58.576
He's a monsignor.

49:58.954 --> 50:01.367
